         {1,4;2,5;3,6}



 -- Function: rowrev x
 -- Function: colrev x
 -- Function: reverse x
     Reverse a matrix. *note rowrev: de. reverses the rows, *note
     colrev: df. the columns, *note reverse: 3a. both dimensions.


